Node:   head_movement
Input:
    int16 degrees
Config:
    max right: 180 degrees
    max left: 0 degrees
    addr: address of servo controller
Output:
    bool success
Steps:
    Initialization: Wait for service requests
    1.  if a request is received, then
            if request type is Track (T), then
                (a) get current position by making a request to the I2S Bus Manager (R,addr)
                (b) send request to I2S Bus Manager (W,addr,current+degrees)
            else
                (a) send request to I2S Bus Manager (W,addr,degrees)